name: BUIDL DAO
description:
BUIDL DAO is a decentralized collaborative organization, The initial goal is to establish a construction of the NFT's infrastructure, and we look forward to the participation of developers interested in the NFT field. The main development direction is NFT synthetic assets, fragmentation, creation, trading, information collection, etc. As a member of BUIDL DAO, Phantom has made explorations in the direction of NFT synthetic assets and fragmented transactions.
